membership:
The EFCI is member of the European Employers Network (EEN), which is organised several times per year by BusinessEurope, and offers a regular platform of information, discussion and exchanges of experience on issues of concern for European employers associations’ representatives. &#xd;
&#xd;
The EFCI participates to the "Liaison Forum", which is organised several times per year by DG Employment of the European Commission, and offers a regular platform of information, discussion and exchanges of experience on subjects of interest for EU social partners’ representatives.
